{"tid":840113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中央底線：不妥協　不流血","createTime":"2018-09-28T12:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T02:35:07.000Z","uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"94f1e43036708eea96c9ecf24da7d965d4640dd1","tid":840113,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20140928/large/a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140928%2Flarge%2Fa1.jpg&h=deccbd56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前國家主席習近平（右）表示支持港府依法處置「破壞秩序的違法活動」。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】面對香港市民及學生激烈的抗爭行動，有建制派人士指出，早前國家主席習近平表示，支持港府依法處置「破壞秩序的違法活動」，意味着北京不會直接插手鎮壓示威，會由港府自行處理。<br />\n而《明鏡新聞》引述北京消息稱，中央應對佔中等抗爭行動，底線是「不妥協，不流血」，不會回應抗爭訴求。<br />\n官方新華社昨有報道香港學生抗爭行動，但只是簡單報道警方拘捕強闖政府總部的61人，以及保安局局長黎棟國等對集會人士強闖政府總部表示遺憾，內文以港府官方立場為依據，強調一切依法行事，未有加入評論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不會動用駐軍鎮壓</span></strong><br />\n有建制派人士表示，習近平早前會見香港富豪和工商界領袖，提及人大常委會對香港政改的決定必須得到尊重，支持港府依法處置「破壞秩序的違法活動」，意味着北京不會因為香港的抗爭而讓步，但也不會如一些建制派所說，動用駐軍直接鎮壓示威，而是讓特區政府自行處理，盡量淡化中央角色。<br />\n《明鏡新聞》引述一位北京派駐港官員指中央應對佔中等抗爭行動，底線是「不妥協，不流血」，又稱北京對控制香港局勢的發展比以前更有信心，指在過去幾個月，國務院港澳辦、國安部等派遣了大量官員來港，掌握第一手資料制訂應對方案，北京判斷港人不願見香港出現混亂，大規模持續、不可控制的抗議活動很難長期維繫，所北京對抗爭並不擔心。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140928/18882345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140928%2F18882345&d=D7p7yELdsgYnL284KuL%2F7J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8489c9c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140928%2F18882345&h=3b422cab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140928/18882345</a>"},{"pid":"c1ce766a38b34737308166de3b33c42ed4190040","tid":840113,"uid":91771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"唔怪得咁耐都唔亮劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a7c916f8934d72464c7b06c0c14f6dbd15dc18","tid":840113,"uid":53705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"北京判斷港人不願見香港出現混亂，大規模持續、不可控制的抗議活動很難長期維繫，所北京對抗爭並不擔心。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3f91424deb6972c146641da59e583e5b1fc5c4","tid":840113,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"有血都比你吸乾吸淨 梗係唔流啦"},{"pid":"f6870bbe99c91fc94a1f44dca67f8f3368f29ba3","tid":840113,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5652d5871d97c5015dcccba648153a2218fc0367","tid":840113,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T02:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2ee7f304565dfbdaa212bee8793b70eea359e2","tid":840113,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T02:34:55.000Z","msg":"又LOOP返去清末 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不戰、不和、不守、不死、不降、不走。"},{"pid":"e95f77b4c8083d7e545248494bbc516cb8317bcd","tid":840113,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1ce766a38b34737308166de3b33c42ed4190040","tid":840113,"uid":91771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:35:51.000Z"